in each of the following
in the banking system.

00:03:53.556 --> 00:03:57.400
So part one is loans, so
what's the maximum change

00:03:57.400 --> 00:04:00.040
over time in the banking system of loans?

00:04:00.040 --> 00:04:01.990
Pause this video, try to figure it out.

